  "name": "rtransparency",
  "description": "Automatically detects ten indicators of research transparency in full-text biomedical articles (PubMed Central JATS XML or plain text): conflict-of-interest disclosure, funding disclosure, protocol registration, novelty, replication or external validation, data sharing, code sharing, disclosure of generative-AI use, open-access licensing, and reporting-guideline use. Each prediction is paired with the exact triggering text, with reproducible accuracy benchmarks.",
